'From Squeakland 3.8.5976 of 25 August 2004 [latest update: #324] on 20 September 2004 at 11:11:05 am'!"Change Set:		ScriptableButton-bfDate:			20 September 2004Author:			Bert FreudenbergperformScriptIfCan: was sent to the morph instead of to the player"!!ScriptableButton methodsFor: 'button' stamp: 'bf 9/20/2004 11:10'!doButtonAction	"The user has pressed the button.  Dispatch to the actual user script, if any."	scriptSelector ifNil: [^ super doButtonAction].	self pasteUpMorph player performScriptIfCan: scriptSelector! !